pluginDNA.description: This plugin helps in deploying the AWS Lambda function and layers build right from the JetBrains IDE. Supports deployment of AWS lambda functions. Supports management of AWS Lambda Layers. Create new versions, delete old versions and update lambda functions to any layer version right from the IDE. Links: Youtube Demo 1 - Initial Launch (25 July, 2020) Youtube Demo 2 - AWS Layers (27 March, 2021) Youtube Demo 3 - AWS SSO (11 June, 2022) Twitter @raevilman [Note]: If in case you update your IDE and this plugin becomes incompatible. Please inform the developer at jetbrains@therdnotes.com rather than leaving negative comment . The plugin will be updated asap.
